Drafter (FISHER/201404/02/SG)
Job ID
EPM-00007622
Country
Singapore
State/Province
Singapore
City
Singapore
Publish Start Date
Apr 29 2014
Job Level
Experienced (Non-Manager)
|
Responsibilities:
Responsible for drafting of Maintenance, Replacement Order (MRO) and Project Orders.
Create and construct Models / Assemblies / Drawings in SolidWorks / Co Create designer, drafter software based on customers’ requirements, specifications, calculations.
Ensure timely maintenance, modification and updating of drawings.
Maintain documents in PDM Works / Work Manager PDM’s.
Work closely with the production and project teams on drawings and make adjustments as necessary.
Requirements:
Diploma / NITEC in Mechanical Engineering or equivalent.
At least 2 years of relevant drafting experience preferably in manufacturing industries.
Proficient in creating 3D CAD models, 2D mechanical drawings and AUTOCAD.